title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 20 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – May 20 2022
description:
The left ramps up its attacks on Elon Musk: After 24 Hours in the GOP, Musk faces sex smear. Clay and Buck remind that Musk predicted they would go after him. Clay says, "Elon Musk has gone from a hero of the left to someone that they are trying to destroy based on simply believing in content neutral policies." Former DNC chair and governor of Vermont Howard Dean calls for boycott of Fox News and deportation of Murdoch family: "They are the enemy of the United States." Princeton president demands tenured professor is fired -- for an old unrelated incident -- after he opposed giving black colleagues more sabbatical time and higher salaries than white staff in wake of BLM movement. Hillary Clinton approved dissemination of Trump-Russian collusion hoax to media, campaign manager testifies.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
